{"word":"διήκω","slug":"διήκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διήκω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ξω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to extend</i> or <i>reach</i> from one place to another, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to go through, pervade</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to pass over</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}